imarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles it also caters to institutions including college endowments charitable foundations and pension plans and high net worth individuals the firm manages separate clientfocused equity portfolios it also manages hedge funds for its clients the firm invests in the public and private debt and equity securities market across the globe with a focus on developed and emerging markets alike it employs strategies such as credit investments longshort equity merger arbitrage real estaterelated investments and direct investments the firm employ value driven approach with a combination of fundamental analysis with bottomup stock picking approach it employs a combination of inhouse and external research to make its investments the firm seeks to make direct investments in private companies specializing in recapitalization and special situations and real estate including office retail multifamily and industrial assets farallon capital management llc was founded in march  and is based in san francisco california detailed description one maritime plazasuite san francisco ca united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwfaralloncapitalcom key executives for farallon capital management llc mr andrew james mclean spokes managing partner age  mr gregory siemon swart managing member and chief financial officer mr mark christopher wehrly jd managing member chief operating officer and special counsel mr matthew trentini managing director and chief technology officer mr david adam posner managing member  global head of ir  business development compensation as of fiscal year  farallon capital management llc key developments essar oil and essar steel fails to meet  deadline for stake sale apr   essar oil ltd and essar global holdings limited belonging to ruia brothers have failed to meet the mar  deadline for their stake sale deals as they are awaiting the approval of lenders farallon capital management llc is interested in acquiring a  stake in